RESEARCH_MUNICIPALITY.notes: Lynnwood, WA operates under a mayor-council government. Christine Frizzell is the current Mayor. The City Council consists of seven members elected at-large. The listed council members are based on the current information available on the City of Lynnwood's official website. Recent election results from November 2025 are still being certified and new terms typically begin in January of the following year, so the currently serving officials are provided.
